帶進囚室，其間庭上多人向被告大叫：「加油呀！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/ANSJN3MEJ5D7HJGPP6A3MHNNRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FANSJN3MEJ5D7HJGPP6A3MHNNRI%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOJFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=a824523f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FANSJN3MEJ5D7HJGPP6A3MHNNRI%2F&h=7b106e03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/ANSJN3MEJ5D7HJGPP6A3MHNNRI/</a>"},{"pid":"3e0a84335406c95821c7202809a28663e14e3fb8","tid":2514385,"uid":260065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39579e2abe69d8c69ce6305c6ff1ae9911182cb","tid":2514385,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"無醫療報告就話攻擊性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e84f634a267943f2398001466c9b6d674a9da13","tid":2514385,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cdf2c23cbb9bf803ed93e0fe80d9d7f48374364","tid":2514385,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41b63a34b2c1173856a0514691e7aa42149f4e8a","tid":2514385,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條J 好快都算係在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"其實西都可以強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以崔美霞都係管有攻擊性武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"管有賣淫工具意圖作出犯法行為."}]}